# IAM Concepts Learned

## 1. Allow Policy

Allow policies provide access permissions.

Examples:
- View bucket
- Upload files
- Read objects

---

## 2. Explicit Deny Policy

Explicit deny policies block access even if another allow policy exists.

Important Rule:
- Explicit Deny always overrides Allow in AWS IAM.

---

## 3. Difference Between Bucket Listing and Direct Bucket Access

Learned that:

### Bucket Listing Permission
Allows user to see bucket list in S3 dashboard.

### Direct Bucket Access
Allows user to open bucket directly using URL if permission exists.

